sdps.name: Novice Trainer
sdps.description: As proof that you completed the Trainer Lord's exercises, you were gifted this.|This panel is very versatile, granting many useful parameters for anyone.
sdps.topFlavorText: Proof that you completed the transdimensional beginner's tutorial.

sdps.name: Veteran Trainer
sdps.description: As proof that you completed the Trainer Lord's exercises, you were gifted this.|This panel is very offensive, granting many parameters geared towards dispatching foes quickly.
sdps.topFlavorText: Proof that you completed the transdimensional intermediate's tutorial.

sdps.name: Enchanter's Guile
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must hone your enchanting guile.
sdps.topFlavorText: Enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Mages' Hands
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must prove your control over the magicks.
sdps.topFlavorText: Further enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Warlock's Thirst
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must sate your thirst.
sdps.topFlavorText: Greatly enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Wizard's Ruin
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must bring ruin.
sdps.topFlavorText: Significantly enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Sorcel's Pledge
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must pledge your soul.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Periapt Pact
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must seal the pact.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Arcane Finesse
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must seal the pact.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Magi Specialist
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must seal the pact.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Master of Sorcery
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi, you must seal the pact.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Hexerei Maximus
sdps.description: To become the True Warmagi... you must ascend.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously enhances the bearer's ability to do magical things.

sdps.name: Fighter's Spirit
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must hone your fighting spirit.
sdps.topFlavorText: Improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Soldiers' Grit
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must prove your grit.
sdps.topFlavorText: Further improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Warrior's Hunger
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must reveal your edge.
sdps.topFlavorText: Greatly improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Berserker Bloodlust
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must intimidate with rage.
sdps.topFlavorText: Significantly improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Oath of Vengeance
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must swear on your oath.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Bloody Promise
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must write your promise with blood.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Combatant Flourish
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must flaunt your talent.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Melee Elitist
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must execute perfectly.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Master of Arms
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord, you must perform masterfully.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Aggression Maximus
sdps.description: To become the True Warlord... you must ascend.
sdps.topFlavorText: Tremendously improves the combat prowess and instincts of the bearer.

sdps.name: Ghosty Presence
sdps.description: Even the ever-iconic ghosty has things you can learn.|Just lean in and listen real good, they whisper dark things and touch your butt.
sdps.topFlavorText: Slaying Ghostys is required in this game. Good job.

sdps.name: Otherworldly Dark
sdps.description: Sometimes, the dead end up reaching back and touching you in ways you don't like-|Like murderously.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Death's Touch" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Spooky Aura
sdps.description: The spooky is an ancient earthen spirit that was laid to rest centuries ago.|Here you are, disturbing its beauty rest like some kind of jackass- seriously, why?!
sdps.topFlavorText: When the going gets tough, the ghosty levels up to a spooky.

sdps.name: Ghastly Plating
sdps.description: The \Enemy[83] somehow are known even in local lands to you, but here they are just armored ghosty foes.|Destroying them is tantamount to your mission.
sdps.topFlavorText: Defeating ghosty enemies is tough, but when they wear armor that is just downright unfair.

sdps.name: Erocian Strong Style
sdps.description: This long-forgotten slime really knew how to wrangle.|The Erocian Strong Style is a reckless style with a goal of maximizing enemy bone breakage.
sdps.topFlavorText: "Slimes just aren't as strong as they used to be." --Rupert

sdps.name: Goo Tango
sdps.description: A slime literally in a dark ass basin apparently had this panel.|This slime doesn't appear different than normal slimes, but Liquify sure does hurt.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Liquify" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Mostly-Seeing Eyes
sdps.description: It was a stretch to call this a slime, but then you see its tentacles.|Known for gorging on bearcats during the winter, apparently.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Brainfog" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Temporal Tactics
sdps.description: While some slimes just absorb your essence through material breakdown,|others are more inclined to melt your face off from another dimension.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Auto-Trudge" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Redhot Blobbing
sdps.description: It is difficult to tell if this was an actual living entity, or just some blob of lava you hacked at for a while.|Either way, its explosions suck so chopping these up is encouraged.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill \Skill[423] when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Sting like a Bee
sdps.description: The lessons learned by all of the slain needlers in the land.|Slaying these pests not only make you feel better, but also help "the people".
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Lunge" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Pressure Points
sdps.description: These appear to be just off-colored Needlers, but they are exponentially more vicious!|The speed of these things is insane, and now yours can be, too.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Venomous Burst" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Drillsation
sdps.description:
Much much more than your average bumblebee, this ruthless stinger has evolved in the harshest of wildernesses to execute even mighty megataurs in a single blow.
Crits truly are deadly and piss everyone off.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn skill when maxed.

sdps.name: Tentacular Touch
sdps.description: Sometimes you just need to reach out and slap a lot of people at once.
sdps.topFlavorText: Whip it good.

sdps.name: Bloody Embrace
sdps.description: The poison of the bloodtrap is extremely dangerous.|Even a few drops can weaken the body enough to be devourable by the trap.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Sap" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Bearfisting It
sdps.description: Why put a glove on it when you can just bearfist it instead?|Bearfisting is an ancient technique passed down from grizzly to grizzly.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Heavy Blow" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Stone's Secret
sdps.description: The panel derived from centuries of breeding. Not selective or anything, just regular ol' breeding.|Probably started with a goal in mind, but ya know, bear urges happened.
sdps.topFlavorText: It was rather difficult finding this panel on the bear considering it had fur made of stone.

sdps.name: Descend into Darkness
sdps.description: A void-consumed bear proved difficult to defeat considering its vast amount of life, but at least|you managed to pry this node from its dead bear mitts.
sdps.topFlavorText: The deepest desires of a bear apparently have always been to descend into darkness.

sdps.name: Orcan Obediance
sdps.description: These orcs were once quite menacing, but clearly your subduing put them into place.|If only you could make use of some of their skills...
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn \Skill[246] when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Orcan Stormcalling
sdps.description: Upper eschelons of orcs are oft heavily intuned with nature, allowing manipulation of the elements.|Thunder is deadly to manipulate, so why not learn it yourself?
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn \Skill[247] when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Orcan Mountaineering
sdps.description:
Orcs that are capable of countering are mean douchebags deserving of getting kicked in the face-
hopefully that was precisely what you did to acquire this node.
sdps.topFlavorText: A deadly orc in the mountains that was very deadly and deadly and also kinda chonky.

sdps.name: Impish Insight
sdps.description: The insight of the kappa is literally dripping with moisture.|Incase you're not sure what that means, neither am I.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Kappa Slap" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: River Runs Deep
sdps.description: In some regions, kappa have come together in a sort of community and begun showing more civilized behavior.|This particular kappa appears to communicate with some sort of higher deity... I wonder if we'll meet them later?
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Energy Beam" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Kappan Dirty Tricks
sdps.description: Not all kappas are magical and worship their deities.|Some are guards for said shamans, and they really like playing dirty.
sdps.topFlavorText: When you're just a shark-man, you sometimes need a dirty trick or two to win.

sdps.name: Resourceful Ratactics
sdps.description: Rats manage to thrive in nearly all environments, including flooded rivers.|Channel your inner rat and get resourceful.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Tumble" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Skies of the Cave
sdps.description: Bats are vicious and obnoxious creatures|They are renowned far and wide for slaying young would-be protagonists.
sdps.topFlavorText: You truly can never chop up enough bats. You're doing the cave a favor.

sdps.name: Soak 'n' Spray
sdps.description: Apparently, this planet has somehow managed to evolve water bats.|We aren't talking about bats that like water, we're talking bats MADE OF WATER.
sdps.topFlavorText: Bats that are made of water are just as stupid as those that aren't.

sdps.name: Crimson Gaze
sdps.description: An ever-iconic eyeball with wings. They can be found all across the universe for some reason.|This one however, appears to be wrapped in flames, which makes it rather annoying to get close to.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill \Skill[248] when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Flame's Caress
sdps.description: When the flames caress you, the power swells within.|It might be something else swelling, though.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill \Skill[214] when this node is maxed.

sdps.name: Yokai Blaze
sdps.description: Killing the already-dead is an impressive feat.|Not like you cared or could even tell since it was taking fiery swings at ya like a douchebag.
sdps.topFlavorText: The wrathful blaze of a dead dead thing is scary.

sdps.name: Bullheaded
sdps.description: Being bullheaded isn't always a bad thing.|He grew to be big and strong from a little cow before you slayed him!
sdps.topFlavorText: Be strong and tenacious like the bull. Or pretend at least.

sdps.name: Ironfist of Iron
sdps.description: The terror of the megataurs are known far and wide.|Deleting them would save hundreds of lives per year.
sdps.topFlavorText: The one with the iron fist of iron will rule.

sdps.name: Pissed Off Sprout
sdps.description: The rage of a sprout (such as a Fungrowth) should never be underestimated.|Never forget.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Rage Growth" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Spiritual Shrooming
sdps.description:
Fungrowths that have ceased to exist actually don't cease to exist in this realm,
they just respawn as ghosty versions and are much more menacing.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn their trademark skill upon maxing this panel.

sdps.name: Flowing Fluids
sdps.description: May the fluids flow and... not ebb, that would be weird. Especially from a Jelli.|Don't do that.
sdps.topFlavorText: The jelly's luminance has been extinguished. ðŸ’”

sdps.name: Jelicious Jaunt
sdps.description: The corpse of this thing has some rather jiggly elements that remind you of a certain other jiggly asset...
sdps.topFlavorText: What a massive fucking jelli carrying around this node.

sdps.name: Scorn of Fae
sdps.description: Fae's have always been the kings of being able to piss you off by throwing rocks at you.|But soon, you too will be able to piss people off by throwing rocks at them!
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn this enemy's trademark skill upon mastering the node.

sdps.name: Unseelie Court
sdps.description: When the unseelie chaos can be encapsulated, it can eventually be converted into a battery to fuel your stats ala this node!
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn this enemy's trademark skill upon mastering the node.

sdps.name: Thief's Code
sdps.description: The thief's code describes all sorts of various rules.|They are really more like guidelines, though.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Shockwave" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Outlaw's Shortcuts
sdps.description: In the north eastern reaches of Erocia, disaster appears to have struck.|Bandits leveled up their game and transcended to outlaws, making your life that much harder.
sdps.topFlavorText: Even bandits need to step up their game from time to time.

sdps.name: Glutton's Dogma
sdps.description: The dogma of the Glutton is held above all else: "thou must satiate thine hunger".
sdps.topFlavorText: This node radiates with a strange energy...

sdps.name: Wrath's Dogma
sdps.description: The dogma of the Wrath is held above all else: "thou must satiate thine rage".
sdps.topFlavorText: This node radiates with a strange energy...

sdps.name: Burrow Burr
sdps.description: An ancient panel with a burr still in it.|Who knows what we'll be able to do with it.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Void Spiral" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Living Volcano
sdps.description: While the burrowing worms are scary, worms that burrow through lava are even more frightening.|Their \Skill[425] is nothing to shake a stick at, so shove that stick down their throat and spare yourself the burns.
sdps.topFlavorText: Why did worms have to become immune to magma and be so aggressive?

sdps.name: Wriggle Dansu
sdps.description:
In the far off mountains there is a legend that worms dance. No one knows why, but it is wildly entertaining to watch.
Watch it once and you'll be addicted to doing it yourself for all eternity.
sdps.topFlavorText: Why can't worms of Erocia just be regular poop-loving soil-burrowing worms?

sdps.name: Boney Situation
sdps.description: The skeleton is an age-old RPG enemy- often frail and wimpy.|These skeletors live up to that expectation in spades.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Backstep" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Spinal Control
sdps.description: When the opportunity to smash up skeletons comes about, one must accept.|Smashing up skeledoggos is no exception to this hardfast rule.
sdps.topFlavorText: The benefits of the dead should be weighed carefully.

sdps.name: Princely Flourish
sdps.description: Regally speaking, one should verily be theoretically flourishing preposterously nonstop.|IndubitiblyðŸ§.
sdps.topFlavorText: Be mindful of the poison, because poison fuckin' hurts and there are no antidotes.

sdps.name: Lamian Royalty
sdps.description: Regally speaking, one should verily be theoretically flourishing preposterously nonstop.|IndubitiblyðŸ§.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Energy Arrow" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Gasp King
sdps.description: Deadly snakes that do deadly things should be made ded faster than they ded you.
sdps.topFlavorText: You dedded this snake so gud.

sdps.name: Dragonic Sacrifice
sdps.description: The dargins of Erocia can vary wildly in shape, size, color, and elemental affinity.|The Lesser Dargins are known for their petite stature, but they are still formidible.
sdps.topFlavorText: Learn the skill "Dargin Flames" when this panel is maxed.

sdps.name: Arctica Chillius
sdps.description: The dargins of Erocia can vary wildly in shape, size, color, and elemental affinity.|The Chilly Wyverns are known for being careful and calculating.
sdps.topFlavorText: Something something witty something.

sdps.name: Titan's Girth
sdps.description: Titans are a mighty race, surpassed only by folks who have guns, because guns obviously.|You really can just end a lot of life if you get good at shooting shit.
sdps.topFlavorText: A mighty foe drops a mighty panel.

sdps.name: Crabtastical Crunchiness
sdps.description: The crabs of Volcanis are no joke, what with them constantly trying to keep you rooted in-place.|It is unclear how they exist in such a hot area without just being cooked by the ambient temperature.
sdps.topFlavorText: Combo crabs are the worst- not even good enough for eating.
